# Doctor & Patient API (FastAPI)

## Description
This project is a simple REST API built using FastAPI to manage Doctors and Patients.

## 🛠 Tech Stack
- Python
- FastAPI
- Pydantic
- Uvicorn

##  How to Run

1. Install packages:
pip install fastapi uvicorn

2. Run server:
uvicorn main:app --reload

3. Open browser:
http://127.0.0.1:8000/docs

### Doctor APIs
- POST /doctors
- GET /doctors
- GET /doctors/{doctor_id}

### Patient APIs
- POST /patients
- GET /patients

##  Validation
- Email must be valid
- Age must be greater than 0